 2023-05252023-06-01AAFC
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder Providing Financial Assistance to Beekeepers in Ontario, Manitoba and Alberta and Grape Producers in Ontario
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada to enter into an AGREEMENT with the PROVINCES OF ONTARIO, MANITOBA AND ALBERTA in order to provide federal contributions of up to $20.1 million to assist beekeepers in Ontario, Manitoba and Alberta and grape producers in Ontario affected by multiple extreme weather events during the winter of 2021-2022.
